industry-lgbt-community-interview.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="BlackPink生产商Sinxity更安全的K-Pop行业LGBT社区访谈" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/blackpink-producer-sinxity-safer-k-pop-industry-lgbt-community-interview.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/blackpink-producer-sinxity-safer-k-pop-industry-lgbt-community-interview-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/blackpink-producer-sinxity-safer-k-pop-industry-lgbt-community-interview-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/blackpink-producer-sinxity-safer-k-pop-industry-lgbt-community-interview-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/blackpink-producer-sinxity-safer-k-pop-industry-lgbt-community-interview-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/blackpink-producer-sinxity-safer-k-pop-industry-lgbt-community-interview-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blackpink">Blackpink的</a>制作人Sinxity对在K-Pop行业工作的同性恋者感到自己的安全性开放，称这“比过去更安全”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/gi-dle-minnie-solo-debut-her-interview-3832435">（G）I-Dle的Minnie违背先入为主的期望：“实际上，这个女孩可以不同”</a></strong></li></ul><p> Sinxity，真实的名字SJ Shin，最近根据他的新女孩团体Cosmosy的首次亮相与<em><a href="https://www.billboard.com/music/features/sinxity-cosmosy-interview-kpop-industry-inclusion-1235898124/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">广告牌</a></em>交谈。韩国音乐主管打破了四人成立，风格概念以及推动宇宙作品的价值观背后的过程。</p><p>在采访中，Sinxity指出了一个人的真实自我的真实联系和表达是他最大的价值观。他分享道：“韩国娱乐业变得比过去更安全。” “因为我是同性恋，身份和多样性对我来说非常重要，而我试图建立的东西。”</p><p>尽管它仍然“不被广泛接受在LGBT社区中”，但对同性恋者的法律和限制，但Sinxity指出，与其他人相比，这是“更加接受，更安全，更好的空间”。他还添加了一个免责声明，说：“出来并公开同性恋并不是一件事情”。</p><p>制片人告诉The Outlet，“我有一个独特的身份，所以我不禁要谈论它，无论如何在这里分享自己，”特别回忆起他作为Blackpink的<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/yg-entertainment">YG Entertainment</a>的制片人的时间。 “我只想自由创建，吸引更多的人并在这些创意领域向他们展示更多。”</p><p>在采访中的其他地方，Sinxity自从<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ador-hybe-feud-timeline-story-3754759">持续的Newjeans-Hybe争执</a>开始以来，也表达了他对乐队及其前首席执行官Min Hee-Jin的支持。他说：“还有一件事：等待<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/newjeans">纽让</a>并站起来，忍受hee-jin。”他是第一位向四面楚歌的前阿多尔<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/ador">（Ador）</a>首席执行官表示公众支持的韩国高管。</p><p> “我真的很佩服敏恩，并尊重她。她是这个K-Pop行业中唯一最好的制作人，所以我真的[想]与她站在一起，并为纽让夫人提供更多免费活动祈祷。”他说。 “我们在一些同一网络中，但我真的只是粉丝。她确实是一个仅有的合格制作人。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blackpink-producer-sinxity-says-the-k-pop-industry-has-become-safer-for-lgbtqia-community-3837269">BlackPink后的生产商Sinxity表示，对于LGBTQIA+社区而言，K-Pop行业已变得“更安全”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
这是“单身地狱”第4季的所有最后夫妇https://www.nme.com/news/tv/here-are-are-are-all-the-final-couples-on-singles-inferno-season-season-4-3837249？最终的夫妻在ferno-inferno季季-4Carmen Chin Wed, 12 Feb 2025 07:59:36 +0000 NewsTV NewsK-popNetflix https://www.nme.com/?p=3837249 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/singles-inferno-final-couples-season-4-contestants-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="单身的地狱最后一对夫妇第4季参赛者" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/singles-inferno-final-couples-season-4-contestants-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/singles-inferno-final-couples-season-4-contestants-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/singles-inferno-final-couples-season-4-contestants-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/singles-inferno-final-couples-season-4-contestants-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/singles-inferno-final-couples-season-4-contestants-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/singles-inferno-final-couples-season-4-contestants-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>两名男性和三名女选手在Inferno上独自结束了本赛季</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/here-are-all-the-final-couples-on-singles-inferno-season-4-3837249">这里的帖子是“单身Inferno”第4季的所有最后夫妇</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/singles-inferno-final-couples-season-4-contestants-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="单身的地狱最后一对夫妇第4季参赛者" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/singles-inferno-final-couples-season-4-contestants-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/singles-inferno-final-couples-season-4-contestants-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/singles-inferno-final-couples-season-4-contestants-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/singles-inferno-final-couples-season-4-contestants-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/singles-inferno-final-couples-season-4-contestants-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/singles-inferno-final-couples-season-4-contestants-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Netflix的热门约会现实系列<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/series/singles-inferno">单曲的Inferno</a></em>刚刚结束了第四季的最后一集 - 这是所有夫妻在第四季成功离开Inferno的夫妇。<b>期望该系列的剧透。</b></p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kpop-concert-tour-music-festival-asia-sea-tickets-dates-3344654">亚洲的K-Pop音乐会，巡回演出和音乐节：Gfriend，J-Hope，Day6等</a></strong></li></ul><p><em>单身的Inferno</em>遵循一群单身人士生活在一个名为Inferno的偏远岛屿上时，他们试图找到爱情，同时让他们的个人细节彼此隐藏。以豪华酒店套房为特征的天堂，将自己脱离岛上并将自己与另一名参赛者配对来找到浪漫的唯一方法。</p><p> 2月11日，Netflix上第四季首映的最后两集，标志着流行约会节目的全新赛季的结论。男性参赛者被要求走向他们想离开岛上的那位女士，总共成功了四对。结果，有两名男性和三名女选手在没有伴侣的情况下结束了本赛季-Kim Jeong-su，Jang Theo，Chung You-Jin，Park Hae-Lin和Kim Min-Seol。</p><h2>以下是在<em>单身地狱</em>第四季一起离开Inferno的夫妇：</h2><h3> Kim Tae-Hwan和Bae Ji-Yeon </h3><figure id="attachment_3837261" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3837261" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3837261" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bae-ji-yeon-kim-tae-hwan-singles-inferno-season-4-finale.jpg" alt="bae ji-yeon kim tae-hwan单人的地狱第4季大结局" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bae-ji-yeon-kim-tae-hwan-singles-inferno-season-4-finale.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bae-ji-yeon-kim-tae-hwan-singles-inferno-season-4-finale-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bae-ji-yeon-kim-tae-hwan-singles-inferno-season-4-finale-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bae-ji-yeon-kim-tae-hwan-singles-inferno-season-4-finale-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bae-ji-yeon-kim-tae-hwan-singles-inferno-season-4-finale-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/bae-ji-yeon-kim-tae-hwan-singles-inferno-season-4-finale-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3837261" class="wp-caption-text"> LR：Bae Ji-Yeon，Kim Tae-Hwan。学分：Netflix</figcaption></figure><p> 25岁的空间设计师Bae Ji-Yeon最终选择了31岁的DJ Kim Tae-Hwan。尽管她对自己对她的感情的真实本质表现出了犹豫，但泰恩（Tae-hwan）选择了吉（Ji-Yeon），并成功地离开了地狱。</p><h3>钟勋和金惠金</h3><figure id="attachment_3837259" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3837259" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3837259" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kim-hye-jin-an-jong-hoon-singles-inferno-season-4-finale.jpg" alt="金惠（Kim Hye-jin An Jong-hoon Single）的地狱第4季大结局" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kim-hye-jin-an-jong-hoon-singles-inferno-season-4-finale.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kim-hye-jin-an-jong-hoon-singles-inferno-season-4-finale-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kim-hye-jin-an-jong-hoon-singles-inferno-season-4-finale-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kim-hye-jin-an-jong-hoon-singles-inferno-season-4-finale-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kim-hye-jin-an-jong-hoon-singles-inferno-season-4-finale-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kim-hye-jin-an-jong-hoon-singles-inferno-season-4-finale-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3837259" class="wp-caption-text"> LR：金正恩（Kim Hye-jin），一个钟。学分：Netflix</figcaption></figure><p>企业主和餐馆老板一个钟勋和模特金·珍（Kim Hye-Jin）互相选择，一起离开了岛屿。值得注意的是，吉杨是本赛季前几集中以钟勋为男性游戏规则改变的女选手之一。</p><h3> Kook Dong-Ho和Kim A-Rin </h3><figure id="attachment_3837260" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3837260" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3837260" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kim-a-rin-kook-dong-ho-singles-inferno-season-4-finale.jpg" alt="Kim A-Rin Kook Dong-Ho单曲Inferno第4季大结局" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kim-a-rin-kook-dong-ho-singles-inferno-season-4-finale.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kim-a-rin-kook-dong-ho-singles-inferno-season-4-finale-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kim-a-rin-kook-dong-ho-singles-inferno-season-4-finale-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kim-a-rin-kook-dong-ho-singles-inferno-season-4-finale-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kim-a-rin-kook-dong-ho-singles-inferno-season-4-finale-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kim-a-rin-kook-dong-ho-singles-inferno-season-4-finale-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3837260" class="wp-caption-text"> LR：Kim A-Rin，Kook Dong-Ho。学分：Netflix</figcaption></figure><p>尽管Kook Dong-ho在第四季的广受欢迎，但这位30岁的会计师和25岁的Model Kim A-Rin通过互相选择包裹了结局。 Dong-Ho与A-Rin和Park Hae-Lin一起被抓住了三角形，他们还将他选为她的最后选择。但是，东霍（Dong-ho）明确表示，他对A-Rin最感兴趣，不太可能改变主意。</p><h3> Yuk Jun-Seo和Lee Si-an </h3><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3837258" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/yuk-jun-seo-lee-si-an-singles-inferno-season-4-finale.jpg" alt="Yuk Jun-Seo Lee Si-An单打Inferno第4季大结局" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/yuk-jun-seo-lee-si-an-singles-inferno-season-4-finale.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/yuk-jun-seo-lee-si-an-singles-inferno-season-4-finale-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/yuk-jun-seo-lee-si-an-singles-inferno-season-4-finale-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/yuk-jun-seo-lee-si-an-singles-inferno-season-4-finale-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/yuk-jun-seo-lee-si-an-singles-inferno-season-4-finale-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/yuk-jun-seo-lee-si-an-singles-inferno-season-4-finale-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>李·西安（Lee Si-An）成为第四季的明星，三名参赛者在本赛季的结局中争夺她：Yuk Jun-Seo，Kim Jeong-su和Jang Theo。这三个人都将Si-An任命为他们的最终选择，但是选择Jun-Seo作为她的Paradise伴侣。</p><p>制片人金·詹（Kim Jae-Won）在接受<em><a href="https://time.com/7221367/singles-inferno-season-4-ending-couples/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《时代》</a></em>采访时透露，他个人对Si-An的最终选择“非常困惑”。他补充说：“当你看到最后一集时，我可以告诉你，[si-an]对她的选择非常认真，她考虑了所有方面，并为她做了正确的选择。”</p><h2>这是在<em>单身地狱</em>第四季中留下单身的参赛者：</h2><h3>张西奥</h3><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="西奥没有后悔|单人的地狱第4季| Netflix [Eng Sub]" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/q93wIAww-TI?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>西奥（Theo）在整个赛季中都对李·西安（Lee Si-An）保持了感情，尽管她告诉他她没有回报他们。尽管如此，他还是将她作为天堂的最后选择，结束了演出的任务，最终被送往岛上。</p><h3>金正日</h3><p>企业家金正日（Kim Jeong-Su）是选择李·西安（Lee Si-An）作为最终选择的三位男选手之一，并且在第四季的最后几集中与Yuk Jun-Seo进行了密切的竞争。但是，Si-An在最后一分钟的决定中选择了Jun-Seo作为她的伴侣，将Jeong-Su单曲留在Inferno上。</p><h3> chung you-jin</h3><p>您在整个赛季中都有一些参赛者的潜力，即与东霍，朱se，钟，钟和钟苏。她先和Jun-seo首先去了天堂，但被关闭了。尽管她与其他参赛者有可能，但他们没有足够的时间互相认识，从而导致她独自一人留在地狱上。</p><p>节目制片人Kim Jae-won在随着<a href="https://time.com/7221367/singles-inferno-season-4-ending-couples/"><em>时间</em></a>的推移采访中说：“我们没有尽可能多的爱情线。” “她是一个非常有吸引力的参赛者，而且她总是对自己的情感坦率。我认为她真的很适合约会表演，但是因为我们没有给她足够的时间来探索她的选择，所以我认为这很可惜。”</p><h3>公园海林</h3><p>Hae-lin是前K-Pop偶像实习生的演员赛中赛季中期的成员之一。她与钟苏和宗霍约会，甚至与后者建立了友谊，但是在东霍拒绝了她并与A-Rin一起前往天堂之后，她的感情被揭示出是单方面的。</p><h3>金敏 - 塞尔</h3><p>尽管本赛季赢得了司仪小组的胜利，但敏塞尔还是无法离开Inferno。她在演出过程中对Jun-Seo产生了感情，但是他对Si-An的兴趣最终赢得了他的胜利。即使知道他不会回报，她仍然选择他作为她的最终选择。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/here-are-all-the-final-couples-on-singles-inferno-season-4-3837249">这里的帖子是“单身Inferno”第4季的所有最后夫妇</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-dropped-by-talent-talent-agents-following-following-anti-semitic-posts-3837245?utm_source = rsss＆source = rss＆utm_medium = rsss间人才 - 遵循犹太人的犹太人Surej SinghWed, 12 Feb 2025 07:52:15 +0000 Music NewsNewsRap https://www.nme.com/?p=3837245 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-3.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在说唱歌手为迪迪（Diddy）表示支持之后，坎耶（Kanye）的工作人员也辞职</p><p>坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次出现<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-dropped-by-talent-agency-following-anti-semitic-posts-3837245">在反犹太职位之后，坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）被人才代理机构撤出</a>。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-3.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>上周在社交媒体上发表了极大的争议，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kanye-west">坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）</a>被他的人才代理机构（Talent Agency）放弃了。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-unaired-footage-fox-news-anti-semitic-comments-3326989">凭借他的“白人生命问题”的特技，坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）终于达到了没有回报的地步？</a></strong></li></ul><p>根据一份<a href="https://variety.com/2025/music/news/kanye-west-dropped-talent-agency-antisemitic-behavior-1236304073/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>综艺</em></a>报道，西部（现在是法律称为Ye）在星期一（2月10日）被他的代理机构，总部位于洛杉矶的33＆West抛弃。在33＆West，坎耶（Kanye）由特工丹尼尔·麦卡特尼（Daniel McCartney）代表，他曾在社交媒体上宣布他和该机构将与说唱歌手断开所有联系。</p><p>根据<em>Variety</em>的报道，麦卡特尼在一个现已具备的Instagram故事中写道，33＆West正在抛弃Kanye“立即有效”，并解释说这是因为“由于他的有害和可恶的言论，我本人Nor 33＆West可以代表。” </p><figure id="attachment_3782073" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3782073" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3782073" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kanye-West.-Credit_-Gotham_GC-Images.jpg" alt="坎耶·韦斯特。学分：哥谭/GC图像" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kanye-West.-Credit_-Gotham_GC-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kanye-West.-Credit_-Gotham_GC-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kanye-West.-Credit_-Gotham_GC-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kanye-West.-Credit_-Gotham_GC-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kanye-West.-Credit_-Gotham_GC-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Kanye-West.-Credit_-Gotham_GC-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3782073" class="wp-caption-text">坎耶·韦斯特。学分：哥谭/GC图像</figcaption></figure><p><a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/kanye-west-talent-agency-drops-him-antisemitic-posts-1235261778/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Rolling Stone</em></a>还报告说，在说唱歌手在周末的进攻性张贴之后，在坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）公司Yeezy（也称为Yzy）工作的一名工作人员退出了该公司。</p><p>据<em>滚石</em>，工作人员被确定为埃里克·库伊（Eric Cui），他曾经是Yeezy的参谋长。 Cui在他的出口中写道：“我喜欢在Yzy工作，因为我相信您的梦想。我相信言论自由……所以我会用言论自由说对妇女和儿童的暴力和犯罪是错误的。”</p><p> CUI的出口是在坎耶（Kanye）上周发布了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-voices-support-for-diddy-and-chris-brown-free-puff-3835815">一系列推文之后，以支持迪迪（Diddy）和克里斯·布朗（Chris Brown），并敦促前者在性虐待指控中被释放</a>。</p><p>在他对迪迪（Diddy）和布朗（Brown）的支持之后 - 后者多次被指控犯有家庭虐待和袭击 - 坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）将在X（以前称为Twitter）上进行推文狂欢，这会使他声称他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-says-he-is-never-apologising-for-my-jewish-comments-and-claims-to-have-dominion-over-bianca-censori-fuck-all-that-woke-shit-3835994">对妻子比安卡·康科里（Bianca Censori）声称“统治”</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-says-he-is-never-apologising-for-my-jewish-comments-and-claims-to-have-dominion-over-bianca-censori-fuck-all-that-woke-shit-3835994">并向犹太社区撤回他的道歉，</a>以对过去的反犹太言论，并宣布自己为“纳粹”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3834380" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3834380" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3834380" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/KanyeWestGrammys-rumour-response.jpg" alt="Kanye West和Bianca Censori参加第67届格莱美奖" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/KanyeWestGrammys-rumour-response.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/KanyeWestGrammys-rumour-response-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/KanyeWestGrammys-rumour-response-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/KanyeWestGrammys-rumour-response-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/KanyeWestGrammys-rumou